nor'west arch
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a delineation between cloud and clear sky that appears with a nor'west wind in Canterbury region.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
